Is that what you want?

508
00:27:08.460 --> 00:27:10.973
I want peace.

509
00:27:10.997 --> 00:27:12.474
But what difference
does it make?

510
00:27:12.498 --> 00:27:14.364
She signs the papers,
Dad, it's all over.

511
00:27:17.169 --> 00:27:19.409
Have you agreed to
start the process with her?

512
00:27:20.405 --> 00:27:21.850
No, but I think we
both understand

513
00:27:21.874 --> 00:27:23.151
where this is all headed.

514
00:27:23.175 --> 00:27:25.220
I've got plans to meet
with my lawyer tomorrow.

515
00:27:25.244 --> 00:27:27.623
Caleb, I want you to
do something for me.

516
00:27:27.647 --> 00:27:29.625
What?

517
00:27:29.649 --> 00:27:32.850
I want you to hold off on
the divorce for 40 days.

518
00:27:34.453 --> 00:27:35.631
Why?

519
00:27:35.655 --> 00:27:39.534
I'm gonna send you
something in the mail,

520
00:27:39.558 --> 00:27:41.918
something that'll take
you that long to do.

521
00:27:42.962 --> 00:27:44.272
What is it?

522
00:27:44.296 --> 00:27:48.110
It's what saved our marriage.

523
00:27:48.134 --> 00:27:51.479
Dad, if this is a religious
thing, I'd rather you didn't.

524
00:27:51.503 --> 00:27:54.683
Look at it as a gift
from your father.

525
00:27:54.707 --> 00:27:57.841
Take one day at a time,
then see what happens.

526
00:27:58.978 --> 00:28:00.321
Please, son.

527
00:28:00.345 --> 00:28:04.425
If for no other
reason, do it for me.

528
00:28:04.449 --> 00:28:06.583
I'm asking as your father.

529
00:28:10.890 --> 00:28:11.867
Forty days?

530
00:28:11.891 --> 00:28:13.824
Forty days.

531
00:28:27.840 --> 00:28:28.817
Eating alone?

532
00:28:28.841 --> 00:28:30.819
Well, hello, Dr. Keller.

533
00:28:30.843 --> 00:28:32.487
Gavin. Gavin, sorry.

534
00:28:32.511 --> 00:28:34.056
How are you? I'm doing well.

535
00:28:34.080 --> 00:28:36.224
I just, uh, need a place
to put my plate down.

536
00:28:36.248 --> 00:28:37.458
Is this spot reserved?

537
00:28:37.482 --> 00:28:39.027
Oh, um, well,
Deidra was supposed

538
00:28:39.051 --> 00:28:40.862
to meet me, but you're
welcome to join us.

539
00:28:40.886 --> 00:28:43.431
Well, if you're gonna twist my
arm, I don't want any trouble.

540
00:28:48.761 --> 00:28:50.806
Are you gonna eat wearing
your clean white coat?

541
