are wearing one these days.

543
00:28:56.235 --> 00:28:59.147
But it's probably not too
smart while I'm eating.

544
00:28:59.171 --> 00:29:01.216
I didn't know doctors
cared about fashion.

545
00:29:01.240 --> 00:29:03.551
Well, we have to keep up
with the attractive fashions

546
00:29:03.575 --> 00:29:05.954
the Public Relations
employees wear.

547
00:29:05.978 --> 00:29:07.589
I see.

548
00:29:07.613 --> 00:29:10.025
Well, since there's only
one person in that category,

549
00:29:10.049 --> 00:29:11.426
I'm sure she'd feel honored.

550
00:29:11.450 --> 00:29:12.427
She should.

551
00:29:12.451 --> 00:29:14.118
She's pretty amazing.

552
00:29:28.467 --> 00:29:31.635
Hey, you look good.

553
00:29:33.906 --> 00:29:35.583
Thanks.

554
00:29:35.607 --> 00:29:38.186
I try to take care of myself.

555
00:29:38.210 --> 00:29:40.310
You like this song?

556
00:29:41.380 --> 00:29:43.413
Oh, yeah.

557
00:29:44.650 --> 00:29:47.129
You feel that?

558
00:29:47.153 --> 00:29:51.121
It's called chemistry,
and we got it.

559
00:29:53.259 --> 00:29:55.137
Wayne won't leave you.

560
00:29:55.161 --> 00:29:57.601
<i>♪ I'm tired of you twisting
