00:30:01.633 --> 00:30:03.278
Hey, man, you
seen my bag in here?

562
00:30:03.302 --> 00:30:05.346
No, I ain't seen it.

563
00:30:05.370 --> 00:30:07.610
All right. It's
probably in my locker.

564
00:30:08.808 --> 00:30:10.218
