like that together?

683
00:37:34.018 --> 00:37:36.297
Man, you done lost your mind.

684
00:37:36.321 --> 00:37:39.234
Terrell, I can
bench 300 right now.

685
00:37:39.258 --> 00:37:40.668
For real?

686
00:37:40.692 --> 00:37:42.937
Why can't we all come to
the same obvious conclusion?

687
00:37:42.961 --> 00:37:44.872
That I am the man.

688
00:37:44.896 --> 00:37:48.309
All I know is the man left
the thermal-imaging device

689
00:37:48.333 --> 00:37:49.544
